caller_intent: Returning a missed call and providing contact information for follow-up.
resolution_steps: Agent Jamie Flippin identifies the missed call from Mark.
Provides Mark's direct office number and office hours (until 5:00 p.m.).
Informs Mark of availability for further assistance.
summary: Agent Jamie Flippin returns a missed call to Mark, providing contact details and office hours but no substantive discussion occurs. The call serves as a follow-up message rather than a problem-solving interaction.
